messages.title: Our Record of Action
messages.content: 22-year campaign: Green belt around Poole, Champion for a safer and cleaner Poole Harbour, Leading the fight to save Poole A&E, Children's Centre and maternity services.

messages.title: Our Promise of More
messages.content: Protect Poole A&E from Conservatives' closure plans, secure a fairer share of funding for local schools, fight to restore proper community policing in Poole.
